title: Andrew Tate and the West’s lost boys
Ask HN: Is there crowd sourced cause effect mind map for changes?
text:
I'm looking for interactive mind maps that are designed to capture cause and effect and behind contributed by a community. Example...

COVID causes pandemic

Pendimic causes lockdown

Lockdown causes boredom

Boredom cause increase in consumption of digital entertainment

Increased demand cause valuation increase

Increasing valuation causes increased ability to raise funding

More money means increased hiring

Higher demand means more higher salaries

Higher salaries causes companies to innovate and offer permanent remote

Permanent remote jobs cause mass relocation from high cost urban areas

......

Point is lot of people with different perspectives can predict or capture what's happening or going to happen and cover lot of bases. Understanding New trends and changes have implications on every level of society.
